{
  "stem": "21089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you could-- legally, you couldn't go through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you have to go to like we call it green border in, in the field.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I decided to go on January-- on December 31st.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the Russian soldiers celebrate the New Year's quite heavy, mainly with vodka and singing and dancing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the same thing was on their borders and their fields as they wouldn't be so active and it wouldn't-- So was-- this was arrangement with some people who would-- the-- the guides through the-- so one, one-- two days before, one evening, I went to one place, and he took me to a farmer.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the farmer, we'd been waiting till the evening when it was dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he-- this was winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was all snow covered very heavy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- so-- Was it still '39?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in '39, December 30-- 31st.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, I said 30, but through the border, we went the night 31st.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to Vilna in January 1st, 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The journey, it was also-- was-- so first night, we went halfway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at night, we're also sleeping at the some other farmer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know where it was, someplace in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the fellow, the guide, which was the guy who owned the sled and two, yeah, myself and some other fellow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's straw on the sled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you could-- it was so cold that we couldn't sit on the straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to run after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After you got warm, you jump on the sled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you-- for a few minutes, you drove and after you-- back and forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so this was the sec-- first, and we had some warm soup, some food over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
